{"data":[{"name":"81:1","price":"太陽が巻き込まれ（、その光を失っ）た時、","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلشَّمۡسُ كُوِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5801,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"idhā al-shamsu kuwwirat ","translations":["When","the sun","is wrapped up","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["idhā","al-shamsu","kuwwirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,1290],[3,1290,2355]]}},{"name":"81:2","price":"また、星々が（その光を失って）落下した時、","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ ٱنكَدَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5802,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-nujūmu inkadarat ","translations":["And when","the stars","fall, losing their luster","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-nujūmu","inkadarat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,680],[2,680,2060],[3,2060,3665]]}},{"name":"81:3","price":"また、山々が動かされ（て、粉々にされ）た時、¹","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ سُيِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5803,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　復活の日*の山々の変化については、洞窟章４７の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-jibālu suyyirat ","translations":["And when","the mountains","are moved away","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-jibālu","suyyirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1670],[3,1670,2705]]}},{"name":"81:4","price":"また、妊娠十ヶ月目の雌ラクダが放ったらかしにされた時、¹","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡعِشَارُ عُطِّلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5804,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「妊娠十ヶ月の雌ラクダ」は、アラブ人にとって、最も大事なものの一つだった。その日はそれすらも構っている余裕はなく、自分のことで手一杯の状態である（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：２２８参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-ʿishāru ʿuṭṭilat ","translations":["And when","the full-term she-camels","(are) left untended","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-ʿishāru","ʿuṭṭilat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,720],[2,720,1850],[3,1850,2775]]}},{"name":"81:5","price":"また、野獣たちが集められた時、¹","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡوُحُوشُ حُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5805,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　復活の日*には、動物でさえも集められ、裁きを受けた後に砂と化せられる（アッ＝サアディー９１２頁参照）。消息章４０の訳注も参照。また、ほかにも「殺される」「一緒くたにされる」という解釈もある（イブン・カスィール８：３３１参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-wuḥūshu ḥushirat ","translations":["And when","the wild beasts","are gathered","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-wuḥūshu","ḥushirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1770],[3,1770,2535]]}},{"name":"81:6","price":"また、海々が溢れ返った時、¹","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡبِحَارُ سُجِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5806,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「海が溢れ返る」ことについては、山章６の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-biḥāru sujjirat ","translations":["And when","the seas","are made to overflow","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-biḥāru","sujjirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,710],[2,710,1730],[3,1730,2795]]}},{"name":"81:7","price":"また、魂が（自分と同様のものと）一緒にされた時、¹","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّفُوسُ زُوِّجَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5807,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　出来事章７とその訳注も参照。ほかにも「魂が肉体に戻される」「魂に行いが結び付けられる」といった解釈もある（アル＝クルトゥビー１９：２３２参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-nufūsu zuwwijat ","translations":["And when","the souls","are paired","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-nufūsu","zuwwijat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,680],[2,680,1980],[3,1980,3065]]}},{"name":"81:8","price":"また、埋められた女児¹が尋ねられた時、","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡمَوۡءُۥدَةُ سُئِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5808,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　生まれた女児を殺すジャーヒリーヤ*の習慣については、家畜章１３７とその訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-mawūdatu su-ilat ","translations":["And when","the female infant buried alive","is asked","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-mawūdatu","su-ilat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,620],[2,620,2070],[3,2070,2955]]}},{"name":"81:9","price":"「彼女は、いかなる罪ゆえに殺されたのか？」と。","arabic":"بِأَيِّ ذَنۢبٖ قُتِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5809,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"bi-ayyi dhanbin qutilat ","translations":["For what","sin","she was killed","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["bi-ayyi","dhanbin","qutilat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,860],[2,860,2670],[3,2670,4175]]}},{"name":"81:10","price":"また、書巻を開かれ（て、各人に差し出され）た時、¹","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلصُّحُفُ نُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5810,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　この「書巻」は、現世での行いの帳簿（ちょうぼ）のこと（ムヤッサル５８６頁参照）。高壁章８の訳注も参照。また、この時の様子については夜の旅章１３－１４、洞窟章４９、真実章１９－２９、割れる章７以降などを参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-ṣuḥufu nushirat ","translations":["And when","the pages","are laid open","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-ṣuḥufu","nushirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,590],[2,590,1360],[3,1360,2195]]}},{"name":"81:11","price":"また、天が剥ぎ取られた時、¹","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ كُشِطَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5811,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　イブラーヒーム*章４８、預言者*たち章１０４、集団章６７とそれらの訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-samāu kushiṭat ","translations":["And when","the sky","is stripped away","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-samāu","kushiṭat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,2980],[3,2980,3775]]}},{"name":"81:12","price":"また、火獄が点火された時、","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَحِيمُ سُعِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5812,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-jaḥīmu suʿʿirat ","translations":["And when","the Hellfire","is set ablaze","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-jaḥīmu","suʿʿirat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,730],[2,730,1710],[3,1710,2735]]}},{"name":"81:13","price":"また、天国が（その住人である敬虔*な者たちに）近づいた時、","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَنَّةُ أُزۡلِفَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5813,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-idhā al-janatu uz'lifat ","translations":["And when","Paradise","is brought near","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-idhā","al-janatu","uz'lifat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,2230],[3,2230,3695]]}},{"name":"81:14","price":"人は、自分が携えて来たもの（善行と悪行）を知る。","arabic":"عَلِمَتۡ نَفۡسٞ مَّآ أَحۡضَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5814,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ʿalimat nafsun mā aḥḍarat ","translations":["Will know","a soul","what","it has brought","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["ʿalimat","nafsun","mā","aḥḍarat",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,890],[2,890,1610],[3,1610,3450],[4,3450,5015]]}},{"name":"81:15","price":"われはまさに、身を隠すものにかけて誓う。¹","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلۡخُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5815,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　アーヤ*１５ー１８までの、アッラー*によるこの誓いについては、整列者章１の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"falā uq'simu bil-khunasi ","translations":["But nay","I swear","by the retreating planets","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["falā","uq'simu","bil-khunasi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1180],[2,1180,3350],[3,3350,5775]]}},{"name":"81:16","price":"つまり、巣に向かって駆けるもの¹にかけて、","arabic":"ٱلۡجَوَارِ ٱلۡكُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5816,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　これは、夜に現れ、昼には見えなくなる星々のこととされるが、「野牛」「カモシカの類」といった解釈もある（イブン・カスィール８：３３６－３３７参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"al-jawāri al-kunasi ","translations":["Those that run","(and) disappear","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["al-jawāri","al-kunasi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1270],[2,1270,3575]]}},{"name":"81:17","price":"また、到来した夜¹にかけて、","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا عَسۡعَسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5817,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「過ぎ去った夜」という解釈もある（前掲書８：３３８参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-al-layli idhā ʿasʿasa ","translations":["And the night","when","it departs","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-al-layli","idhā","ʿasʿasa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,960],[2,960,1720],[3,1720,2895]]}},{"name":"81:18","price":"また、息づいた朝にかけて。","arabic":"وَٱلصُّبۡحِ إِذَا تَنَفَّسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5818,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-ṣub'ḥi idhā tanaffasa ","translations":["And the dawn","when","it breathes","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-ṣub'ḥi","idhā","tanaffasa",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1150],[2,1150,1680],[3,1680,3185]]}},{"name":"81:19","price":"本当にそれ（クルアーン*）は、まさしく高貴な御使い（ジブリール*）の（伝達する）言葉。","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوۡلُ رَسُولٖ كَرِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5819,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu laqawlu rasūlin karīmin ","translations":["Indeed, it","(is) surely a word","(of) a Messenger","noble","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","laqawlu","rasūlin","karīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1610],[2,1610,2520],[3,2520,3670],[4,3670,5985]]}},{"name":"81:20","price":"力みなぎる者、御座¹のもとで位高き者、","arabic":"ذِي قُوَّةٍ عِندَ ذِي ٱلۡعَرۡشِ مَكِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5820,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「御座」に関しては、高壁章５４の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"dhī quwwatin ʿinda dhī al-ʿarshi makīnin ","translations":["Possessor of","power","with","(the) Owner of","the Throne","secure","(20)"],"transliterationArr":["dhī","quwwatin","ʿinda","dhī","al-ʿarshi","makīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,1460],[3,1460,2430],[4,2430,2580],[5,2580,3460],[6,3460,5415]]}},{"name":"81:21","price":"（他の天使*たちに）追従される者で、誠実な者の（伝達する言葉である）。","arabic":"مُّطَاعٖ ثَمَّ أَمِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5821,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"muṭāʿin thamma amīnin ","translations":["One to be obeyed","and","trustworthy","(21)"],"transliterationArr":["muṭāʿin","thamma","amīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1580],[2,1580,2760],[3,2760,4885]]}},{"name":"81:22","price":"そして、あなた方の同胞（ムハンマド*）は、憑かれた者¹などではなく、","arabic":"وَمَا صَاحِبُكُم بِمَجۡنُونٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5822,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「憑かれた者」については、アル＝ヒジュル章６の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā ṣāḥibukum bimajnūnin ","translations":["And not","(is) your companion","mad","(22)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","ṣāḥibukum","bimajnūnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,580],[2,580,2470],[3,2470,5065]]}},{"name":"81:23","price":"彼は確かに彼（ジブリール*）を、明瞭な地平線上に見たのである。¹","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ رَءَاهُ بِٱلۡأُفُقِ ٱلۡمُبِينِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5823,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　これは預言者*が、初めてジブリール*をその本来の姿で見た時のこととされる（ムヤッサル５８６頁参照）。詳しくは星章７の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"walaqad raāhu bil-ufuqi al-mubīni ","translations":["And certainly","he saw him","in the horizon","the clear","(23)"],"transliterationArr":["walaqad","raāhu","bil-ufuqi","al-mubīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,760],[2,760,1710],[3,1710,2760],[4,2760,5235]]}},{"name":"81:24","price":"また、彼（ムハンマド*）は不可視の世界¹について、出し惜しみする者などではなく、","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ عَلَى ٱلۡغَيۡبِ بِضَنِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5824,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　ここでの「不可視の世界*」とは、啓示を伝達すること（前掲書、同頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā huwa ʿalā al-ghaybi biḍanīnin ","translations":["And not","he (is)","on","the unseen","a withholder","(24)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","huwa","ʿalā","al-ghaybi","biḍanīnin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,610],[2,610,940],[3,940,1420],[4,1420,2330],[5,2330,5085]]}},{"name":"81:25","price":"それ（クルアーン*）は、追放された¹シャイターン*の言葉などではない。","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ بِقَوۡلِ شَيۡطَٰنٖ رَّجِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5825,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「追放された」については、イムラーン家章３６の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā huwa biqawli shayṭānin rajīmin ","translations":["And not","it","(is the) word","(of) Shaitaan","accursed","(25)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","huwa","biqawli","shayṭānin","rajīmin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,1010],[3,1010,1800],[4,1800,2620],[5,2620,3765]]}},{"name":"81:26","price":"ならば、あなた方は（こお明白な論拠の後、）どこへ向かうのか？¹","arabic":"فَأَيۡنَ تَذۡهَبُونَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5826,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　これは、クルアーン*を噓呼ばわりすることに対する非難の言葉（前掲書、同頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ayna tadhhabūna ","translations":["So where","are you going","(26)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ayna","tadhhabūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,710],[2,710,3155]]}},{"name":"81:27","price":"それは、全創造物への教訓に外ならないというのに。","arabic":"إِنۡ هُوَ إِلَّا ذِكۡرٞ لِّلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5827,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"in huwa illā dhik'run lil'ʿālamīna ","translations":["Not","it","(is) except","a reminder","to the worlds","(27)"],"transliterationArr":["in","huwa","illā","dhik'run","lil'ʿālamīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,420],[2,420,800],[3,800,1670],[4,1670,2300],[5,2300,5255]]}},{"name":"81:28","price":"あなた方の内、（真理の上を）まっすぐ歩むことを望んだ者への。","arabic":"لِمَن شَآءَ مِنكُمۡ أَن يَسۡتَقِيمَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5828,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"liman shāa minkum an yastaqīma ","translations":["For whoever","wills","among you","to","take a straight way","(28)"],"transliterationArr":["liman","shāa","minkum","an","yastaqīma",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1520],[2,1520,3140],[3,3140,4340],[4,4340,4640],[5,4640,8225]]}},{"name":"81:29","price":"そしてあなた方は、全創造物の主*であられるアッラー*がお望みにならない限り、（いかなることも）望むことがないのだ。¹","arabic":"وَمَا تَشَآءُونَ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُ رَبُّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5829,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　包る者章５６の、同様の件（くだり）の訳注も参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā tashāūna illā an yashāa al-lahu rabbu al-ʿālamīna ","translations":["And not","you will","except","that","wills","Allah","Lord","(of) the worlds","(29)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","tashāūna","illā","an","yashāa","al-lahu","rabbu","al-ʿālamīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,600],[2,600,3030],[3,3030,4560],[4,4560,4990],[5,4990,6970],[6,6970,8110],[7,8110,8700],[8,8700,12375]]}}],"chapter":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir","Chapter At-Takwir","Takwir","Surah Takwir","Chapter Takwir","At Takwir","Surah At Takwir","Chapter At Takwir","Surah 81","Chapter 81","The Overthrowing","التكوير"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}